ygData.messageBody:
> Yes, I saw this also. Just one thing to say ... that guide (Camii)
> is not the best guide in the world.

Camii, ugh.

> Of course, this was Camii on the E'ci server, I would assume
> that would be the same person?

It's the same idiot person. Camii is the lead GM on Innoruuk
now. It's all going downhill from here people. However, there
is a killer GM on Innoruuk whose name escapes me, or rather will
remain confidential because I don't want to see this guy get booted
like our last head GM did. The good people always are forced to
leave. Anyway, this guy rolls up into PoF and is making me laugh
like every 5 mins. Saying crap like, hey Soandso isn't about time
you eat another DT. The guy was nutz, he was very friendly and
really could fit in with the players though. Shoulda asked him to
pull Cazic for us, heh. He seemed kinda new to the scene however.

Harmonic.
